This builds directly on the Monad Research Kernel architecture by adding:
- Meta-strategy database (vector storage of problem types and successful approaches)
- Performance analytics layer
- Dynamic strategy selector
- Cross-domain pattern matcher

The system remains evolutionary and multi-agent at its core, but now with an intelligent "conductor" that learns which orchestration patterns work best for different research challenges.

